==================================================
POST-MVP EXPANSION LAYER
CONTRACT EXECUTION PIPELINE & WORKFLOW ENGINE
==================================================

PURPOSE:
The platform must understand that many government contracts are not simple one-time deliverables.

Many opportunities represent:
- operational pipelines
- recurring workforce systems
- multi-phase delivery systems
- certification ecosystems
- long-term operational programs

The platform should analyze:
“How does this contract actually operate over time?”

==================================================
CORE PHILOSOPHY
==================================================

The platform should NOT treat contracts as:
- single events
- isolated tasks
- simple deliverables

The platform SHOULD understand:
- operational workflows
- delivery phases
- recurring iterations
- staffing pipelines
- training pipelines
- certification flows
- long-term operational burden

==================================================
CONTRACT EXECUTION PIPELINE ENGINE
==================================================

PURPOSE:
Break contracts into operational execution stages.

The system should map:
- how work flows
- how services repeat
- how staffing scales
- how delivery occurs
- where operational bottlenecks exist

==================================================
CORE EXECUTION PHASES
==================================================

The platform should identify:

1. Acquisition Phase
2. Onboarding Phase
3. Operational Setup Phase
4. Delivery Phase
5. Validation / Testing Phase
6. Certification Phase
7. Sustainment Phase
8. Reporting Phase
9. Renewal / Recompete Phase

==================================================
WORKFORCE PIPELINE DETECTION
==================================================

The system should detect contracts involving:
- training pipelines
- certification programs
- apprenticeship systems
- workforce development
- recurring student throughput
- operational readiness pipelines

EXAMPLES:
- medical training
- military certification
- technical apprenticeships
- operational readiness programs

==================================================
PIPELINE COMPLEXITY ENGINE
==================================================

PURPOSE:
Estimate operational workflow complexity.

FACTORS:
- number of phases
- recurring iterations
- staffing dependencies
- credentialing requirements
- facility requirements
- clinical requirements
- operational continuity
- scheduling complexity
- throughput volume

OUTPUT:
Pipeline Complexity Score
0-100

==================================================
RECURRING ITERATION ANALYSIS
==================================================

The system should detect:
- recurring class cycles
- recurring procurement cycles
- recurring staffing rotations
- recurring operational phases

EXAMPLES:
- 15 iterations annually
- new classes every 3 weeks
- annual recompetes
- rolling intake schedules

==================================================
THROUGHPUT ANALYSIS ENGINE
==================================================

PURPOSE:
Estimate operational throughput.

EXAMPLES:
- students per class
- annual throughput
