==================================================
CONTRACT STABILITY ENGINE
==================================================

PURPOSE:
Estimate long-term market stability.

LOW STABILITY:
- one-time procurement
- one-off construction
- temporary acquisition

HIGH STABILITY:
- workforce training
- operational staffing
- recurring healthcare programs
- certification pipelines

==================================================
RECURRING REVENUE ANALYSIS
==================================================

The system should estimate:
- recurring revenue likelihood
- recompete frequency
- annual renewal patterns
- sustainment opportunities

==================================================
OPERATIONAL DEPENDENCY SCORE
==================================================

PURPOSE:
Estimate how dependent the agency becomes on successful contractor execution.

HIGH DEPENDENCY EXAMPLES:
- medical workforce pipelines
- financial verification systems
- mission-critical staffing

LOW DEPENDENCY EXAMPLES:
- office supplies
- commodity procurement

==================================================
PIPELINE FAILURE IMPACT ENGINE
==================================================

The platform should estimate:
“What happens if this operational pipeline fails?”

LOW IMPACT:
- delayed procurement

HIGH IMPACT:
- reduced military medical staffing
- certification backlog
- readiness degradation

==================================================
